Testing Python - Applying Unit Testing, TDD, BDD, and Acceptance Testing by David Sale.

Setup:
https://virtualenv.pypa.io/en/latest/installation.html
http://virtualenvwrapper.readthedocs.org/en/latest/
pip install nose - run tests
pip install nose-cov - code coverage
pip install rednose - coloring tests
pip install pytest - another way to run tests
pip install pytest-cov - code coverage with pytest
pip install mock - install mock library
pip install requests - requests library for calling REST services


Reference Links:
https://docs.python.org/2/library/unittest.html
https://docs.python.org/2/library/pdb.html
http://learnpythonthehardway.org
